Go to folder where testcases are located
behave -f allure_behave.formatter:AllureFormatter -o allure_result_folder

Folder gets created by folder name i give about for the allure results

allure serve allure_result_folder
 
Above command converts the json o/p files to a html test report, with TRACE for errors 

ssteps to setup allure:
---------------------------
pip install allure-behave

Setup allure through powershell, following steps below.

Run allure from cmd pmt to see it's installed. If java errors, install jdk/jre, set java_home environment variable following steps below:
https://daisy.github.io/pipeline/Get-Help/Troubleshooting/Common-Errors-Windows/

https://winaero.com/blog/find-powershell-version-windows/